data.name: Ocean Dragon Lord - Neo-Daedalus
data.desc: This card cannot be Normal Summoned or Set. This card cannot be Special Summoned except by Tributing 1 "Levia-Dragon - Daedalus". You can send "Umi" you control to the Graveyard to send all cards in both players' hands and on the field to the Graveyard, except this card.

card_sets.set_name: Structure Deck: Fury from the Deep
